&lt;img width="1179" height="1065" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/bf86f44e-c02d-4809-a2b3-05f538acb323" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;the paper was written very well
ㅎㅎㅎㅎ&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>